cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and its efficient implementation on distributed systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses communication protocols and algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of sparsity in communication patterns and updates also indicates a potential fit for cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
